    "We have already investigated the issue of unclear benefits through a systematic literature review extended by a qualitative survey, and our work has been published [84].",
    "This paper details the methodology, presents all findings of the systematic literature review, which includes the findings related to use cases and benefits, and adds further literature about pre-RS traceability published between 2020 and 2022.Pre-RS traceability is also relevant in agile projects [19,44,95].",
    "In agile projects, user stories are commonly used to document requirements that need to be implemented.",
